name: 47 BRAND | SAN FRANCISCO GIANTS SNAPBACK
description:
San Francisco Giants Snapback
By '47 Brand


Features a large team wordmark across the front accompanied with the Giants logo. With the team logo on the side as well, people will know who you're pulling for from every angle! 

The snapback adjustability not only ensures a comfortable fit but is the hot new look that is back and here to stay! 

Quality construction that is expected from '47 Brand
Unique styling
Snapback Adjustable
Officially licensed by MLB

Available In:
WHITE x BLACK
